== 發行 ==
《阿公當家》最初定於2018年2月23日由[[温斯坦影业|温斯坦影业]]的[[次元影業|次元影業]]在美國發行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/01/weinstein-company-release-date-war-with-grandpa-upside-mary-magdalene-1202263517/|title=Weinstein Company Pulls ‘War With Grandpa’, ‘The Upside’ & ‘Mary Magdalene’ Off Release Schedule|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Erik|last=Pederson|date=2018-01-19|accessdate=2018-01-19|archive-date=2018-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180120044448/http://deadline.com/2018/01/weinstein-company-release-date-war-with-grandpa-upside-mary-magdalene-1202263517/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Aug2017V">{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Robert De Niro’s Comedy ‘War With Grandpa’ Gets February Release|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/robert-deniro-war-with-grandpa-february-release-1202535874/|accessdate=2018-08-23|work=Variety|date=2017-08-22|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143858/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/robert-deniro-war-with-grandpa-february-release-1202535874/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後改於2018年4月21日；但由於主要拍攝位置的變化，後來又推遲至2018年10月20日<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=Weinstein Co./Dimension’s Robert De Niro Family Comedy ‘War With Grandpa’ Breaks Out Next Spring|url=https://deadline.com/2016/07/war-with-grandpa-robert-de-niro-release-date-spring-2017-1201785658/|accessdate=2016-10-24|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=2016-07-12|archive-date=2017-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823072727/http://deadline.com/2016/07/war-with-grandpa-robert-de-niro-release-date-spring-2017-1201785658/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Evans|first1=Greg|title=TWC/Dimension Moves Robert De Niro Comedy ‘War With Grandpa’ To October, Sets ‘Polaroid’ For Summer|url=https://deadline.com/2016/12/twc-dimension-war-with-grandpa-release-date-postpone-robert-de-niro-polaroid-1201863671/|accessdate=2017-06-10|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=2016-12-02|archive-date=2017-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815201124/http://deadline.com/2016/12/twc-dimension-war-with-grandpa-release-date-postpone-robert-de-niro-polaroid-1201863671/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年3月，温斯坦影业不再持有該片的發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/weinstein-company-paddington-2-earnings-1202731458/|title=Weinstein Company Made $38.5 Million Selling ‘Paddington 2,’ Other Films|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Brent|last=Lang|date=2018-03-20|accessdate=2018-03-20|archive-date=2018-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180320230848/http://variety.com/2018/film/news/weinstein-company-paddington-2-earnings-1202731458/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並由製片人以250萬美元的價格收回其版權<ref>{{cite web |last=Geier |first=Thom |url=https://www.thewrap.com/weinstein-co-fire-sale-robert-de-niro-war-with-grandpa-sold-back-2-5-million |title=Weinstein Co Fire Sale: Robert De Niro's 'The War With Grandpa' Sold to Producers for $2.5 Million |publisher=Thewrap.com |date=2018-03-20 |accessdate=2019-03-03 |archive-date=2019-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828143826/https://www.thewrap.com/weinstein-co-fire-sale-robert-de-niro-war-with-grandpa-sold-back-2-5-million/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年6月，{{lang|en|101 Studios}}取得了該片的美國發行權，並將其設定為2020年9月18日發行；後來又延遲至10月9日<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/06/robert-de-niro-comedy-the-war-with-grandpa-theatrical-release-1202972683/|title=Robert De Niro Comedy ‘The War With Grandpa’ Eyes October Wide Release Via 101 Studios – Update|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2020-08-13|accessdate=2020-08-13|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806115140/https://deadline.com/2020/06/robert-de-niro-comedy-the-war-with-grandpa-theatrical-release-1202972683/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反響 ==
=== 票房 ===
在美國上映的首日，《阿公當家》在2250家影院中取得110萬美元的票房。該片以以360萬美元的票房登上首週票房冠軍，勝過了蟬連五週冠軍的《[[天能|天能]]》<ref name=DeadlineOpening>{{cite web |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |date=2020-10-11 |url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/war-with-grandpa-hocus-pocus-coco-leaving-footprint-with-families-at-weekend-box-office-1234595173/ |title=‘War With Grandpa’, ‘Hocus Pocus’ & ‘Coco’ Leaving Footprint With Families At Weekend Box Office |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2020-10-11 |archive-date=2020-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010180851/https://deadline.com/2020/10/war-with-grandpa-hocus-pocus-coco-leaving-footprint-with-families-at-weekend-box-office-1234595173/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name= Brueggemann-Oct2020>{{cite news |date= 2020-10-11 |last= Brueggemann |first= Tom |title= ‘Tenet’ No Longer #1 as ‘The War With Grandpa’ Wins Weekend Box Office With $3.6 Million |url= https://www.indiewire.com/2020/10/tenet-the-war-with-grandpa-wins-weekend-box-office-1234592050/ |website= [[IndieWire|IndieWire]] |accessdate= 2020-10-11 |archive-date= 2020-10-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201012093705/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/10/tenet-the-war-with-grandpa-wins-weekend-box-office-1234592050/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《阿公當家》所獲評價不佳，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據119調專業評論，給予29%的好評度，平均分數4.4/10，共識評論寫道：「非常有趣，但更多是被誤導，《阿公當家》將給觀眾留下一些輕笑，還有很多關於這個才華橫溢的演員在想什麼的問題」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_war_with_grandpa|title=The War With Grandpa (2020)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango_Media|Fandango]]|access-date={{RT data|access date}}|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116203417/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_war_with_grandpa|archive-date=November 16, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則根據23條專業評論，獲得平均34分（滿分100分）的加權平均分數，代表「負面評價為主」<ref>{{cite web |title= The War with Grandpa Reviews |url= https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-war-with-grandpa |website= [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |access-date= October 16, 2020 |archive-date= November 16, 2020 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201116203523/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-war-with-grandpa |url-status= live }}</ref>。根據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]的調查，觀眾在A+至F的評分標準中，給予該片「B+」的平均分數。

